  <brief_title>Effects of Gum Chewing on Recovery of Bowel Function Following Benign Gynecologic Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Gum Chewing on Recovery of Bowel Function Following Benign Gynecologic Surgery: a Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
